Professional Recommendations:
{chr(10).join(f'â€¢ {rec}' for rec in results.recommendations)}

{'Critical Issues:' + chr(10) + chr(10).join(f'ğŸš¨ {issue}' for issue in results.critical_issues) if results.critical_issues else 'âœ… No critical issues detected'}

Training Readiness: {'ğŸš€ READY FOR PRODUCTION TRAINING' if results.format_compliance and results.annotation_quality > 90 else 'âš ï¸ REQUIRES ATTENTION'}
"""
        return report

